 {'action': 'created', 'author': 'ChristinFrohne', 'comment_id': 494361265.0, 'datetime': '2019-05-21 12:01:06+00:00', 'masked_author': 'username_1', 'text': 'Here is the text for the site: 

Gitpod: 
Gitpod is an online one-click IDE that launches ready-to-code dev environments from any GitHub page. Automating development environments eliminates hours of tedious setup time, improves teamwork, and makes software development more reproducible and scalable. 

We started developing Gitpod about 2 years ago and this April we officially launched it. Gitpod is a very young product which gives you lots of opportunities to shape its future. Currently we‚Äôre working in a team of less than 20 people and we‚Äôre planning to grow continually. 

Typefox:
TypeFox is the company behind Gitpod with a team of developer tool specialists and longtime contributors to many open-source projects. We‚Äôre a driving force behind the language server protocol and initiators of Eclipse Theia, the next generation IDE that powers Gitpod. A characteristic of our team is a fervour to learn new things. We‚Äôre convinced that missing knowledge shouldn‚Äôt hold one back, but encourage us to learn more. 

Team:
We‚Äôre a young and tech-driven team with the mission of creating developer tools for everyone. In our team we seek for an open and honest mindset, as well as an effective pragmatism. We lead, collaborate and contribute for open-source projects and would love to share that with you. We‚Äôre convinced that continuous learning and exploring is the way to go for sustainably building the best solutions. Therefore we‚Äôre always curious about new approaches.', 'title': None, 'type': 'comment'}
